      "source": [
        "# recogninzing fighter jets with fast.ai"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab_type": "code",
        "id": "66rWU5Z08RYx",
        "colab": {}
      },
      "source": [
        "from fastai.vision import *\n",
        "from google.colab import drive\n",
        "drive.mount('/content/drive')"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "colab_type": "text",
        "id": "OqruCkUtElB0"
      },
      "source": [
        "all the code used for this project can be found on this github page \n",
        "https://github.com/belke05/classifying_fighter_jets\n",
        "_____\n",
        "\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ybmK1WER7u2E",
        "colab_type": "text"
      },
      "source": [
        "<h3>1. create new folders</h3>\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "based upon the csv files created via the JavaScript code"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab_type": "code",
        "id": "nEC8b-ae9yx7",
        "outputId": "aee10e2e-aa91-47ed-b91f-2ef655218f7e",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 34
        }
      },
      "source": [
        "path = Path('/content/drive/My Drive/fastai_classification')\n",
        "\n",
        "for file, folder in [('csv_f16.csv', 'f16'), ('csv_f22.csv', 'f22'), \n",
        "                     ('csv_f35.csv', 'f35')]:\n",
        "    dest = path/'jets'/folder # path + '/' + folder\n",
        "    dest.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n",
        "    download_images(path/file, dest)"
      ],
      "execution_count": 0,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "/content/drive/My Drive/fastai_classification\n"
          ],
          "name": "stdout"
        }
      ]
    },

      "metadata": {
        "colab_type": "text",
        "id": "hjoAKfREJAeq"
      },
      "source": [
